  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Located just at the foot of the slopes with skiing to and from the doorstep, the Hotel MMV Les Neiges is perfectly positioned for exploring the Three Valleys ski area. It offers great value for money with buffet meals included and free wine with evening meals The hotel has a large south facing sun terrace with incredible views of the surrounding mountains, a bar and lounge area for relaxation, restaurant, ski storage and free Wi-Fi in the communal areas. It is an excellent choice for keen skiers who want to discover this incredible ski area.</span></p>]]></description>
